<facsimile><graphic url="https://www.e-manuscripta.ch/i3f/v20/1038088/manifest"/></facsimile><text><body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038089" n="1"/> 
<opener><lb/><salute>Plurimum Reverendo et Clarissimo
  <lb/>Viro <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Michaeli Angelo Far<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dell<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>S.P.D.</abbr> <rs type="person">N.B.</rs></salute></opener>
<p><lb/><date>Hesterno die</date>, eo ipso tempore quo scriptioni ad <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissimum</expan></choice> Domin<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
         <lb/>Doctorem <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottum</rs> operam dabam <rs type="lostletter">literis</rs> Ejus alias ad Te<note type="editorial">Dieses Antwortschreiben von Nic. I B. wurde durch den vorliegenden Brief überflüssig und ist somit wohl nicht erhalten.</note>
  <lb/>inclusurus, accepimus <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus meus</rs> et ego humanissimas
  <lb/>et perquam officiosas <rs type="letter">epistolas</rs> Tuas, quibus quanta opera
  <lb/>et ardore vocationem meam ad Cathedram Mathematicam
  <lb/>in Illustri <rs type="organisation">Archilyceo Patavino</rs> promovere ind<del><gap/></del><add>esinenter</add> studeas,
  <lb/>su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o cum gaudio et voluptate intelleximus.<del></del>
  <lb type="deleted"/><del></del>
  <lb/><del></del>Est quod mihi impense gratuler Tibique quam
  <lb/>maximas gratias agam <del></del><add>de favore tuo per</add> tant<del></del><add>a</add> benefici<del></del><add>a</add> mihi demonstrato
  <lb break="no"/><del></del>, de quo diutinum silentium meum nihil <choice><sic>dem</sic><corr>demi</corr></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sisse l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus agnosco. Ignosces qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so quod ad priores Tuas
  <lb/><del></del>urbanissimis et perquam honorificis expressionibus
  <lb/>refertas <rs key="B_991170517059105501" type="letter">literas</rs>,<note type="editorial">Fardella an Nic. I B. von <rs key="B_991170517059105501" type="letter">1713.11.26</rs>.</note> qua<del></del><add>s</add> <date>ultimis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teriti a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>i diebus</date> acceperam,
  <lb/>citius non responderim.<del></del>
  <lb/><del></del>Scriptionem ad Te et ad <abbr>Dn<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></abbr>
  <lb/><rs type="person">Michelottum</rs> impediebant negotia et Exercitia quadam,<del></del>
  <lb/>quorum in <rs type="organisation">Academia nostra</rs> habendorum mihi data fuit occasio.
  <lb/>Illustris <rs type="person">Leibnitii</rs> nostri co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endationes et auxilia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
  <lb/>continuis suis exhortationibus negotio nostro affert, non minori
  <pb facs="1038090" n="2"/>
  <lb/>gratiarum actione prosequor. Ejus consilium de <rs type="person">Patruo</rs> meo <rs type="place">Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tavium</rs> evocando optimum esse fateor, sed <rs type="person">Patruum</rs> propter
  <lb/>res suas domesticas nonnisi lautissimis et perquam honorifi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cis conditionibus oblatis hinc abiturum credo. <del></del><add>Non ita pridem</add> enim Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fessionem Matheseos <rs type="place">Lugduni Batavorum</rs> <add>cum</add> stipendio mille du<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>catorum sibi oblatam respuit, quamvis <del></del><add>pro</add> <del></del><add>le</add>ctionibus priva<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis <choice><orig>(</orig><reg type="deleted"/></choice>adhuc alterum fere tantum (quales ut audio <rs type="place">Patavii</rs> null<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>habentur) habere potuisset. Ipse autem sententiam suam Tibi
  <lb/>perscribere non cessabit. Interim negotium, de cujus felici
  <lb/>successu haud levem spem nobis injicis, porro <add>Tibi</add> co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatum
  <lb/>habe; <del></del><add>Excellentissimis etiam</add> Viris, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1037004566">Petro Grimani</rs>, <rs type="person">Bernardo
    <lb/>Trevisani</rs>, <rs type="person">Antonio Ruzzini</rs>, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipu<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> <del></del><add>ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice></add> Excellen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissimo Domino Procuratori <rs type="person">Ruzzino</rs> <add>reliquisque <del></del>caus<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Patronis</add> quos omnes rem no<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stram benigne hactenus juvisse nuntiasti, meo nomine ubi
  <lb/>occasio se feret su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>as gratias agere ne dedigneris.<del></del>
  <lb/><del></del>Salutem <del></del><add>Tuam</add> <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person">Herma<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>o</rs> nostro, qui ut
  <lb/>audio munus suum <rs type="place">Francofurti</rs> maximo cum applausu obit,
  <lb/>cum scribam mittere non negligam.</p> <closer><salute>Vale et mihi fave.</salute>
    <lb/><dateline><date when="1719-02-14">14. <abbr>Febr.</abbr> 1719</date>.</dateline> </closer> 
</div></body></text></TEI>